metadata.name: Skylight
metadata.description:
The architecture in London really draws my eye and lookup shots always show it off. I was wandering along south of the river near Tower Bridge and came across these triangular buildings. At first, I didnâ€™t look up and was shooting along the buildings. But when I did, it opened a whole new opportunity. The symmetry was perfect, blue bursting through whispers of cloud, creating my favourite lookup shot.

Title: Skylight

Edition: 1/1

Collection: Journeys Through London
